{"tid":2530664,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「真愛無罪」70歳港伯娶大陸嫩妻：洗咩理黃屍！我仲健康！","createTime":"2021-05-14T14:39:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T16:11:01.000Z","uid":219635,"like":81,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"2e5c99ca4f26a5dcaaaaecbf62f154f4bf1aef1c","tid":2530664,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"孤獨老人&mdash;清潔工住30呎劏房 72歲再婚娶大陸老婆想有人陪終老：<span class=\"red\">老了也有性需要 <br />\n「放假就自己一個人到公園坐，有工開仲好，有寄託。」72歲的許生是一名獨居長者，做清潔工月入約$10,000，</span>住在30呎的劏房，處於貧窮線以下；他的現況，就如日本學者藤田孝典對「下流老人」的定義，像只能活在河流下游的魚。<br />\n<br />\n這天早上7時未到，許生已經到達觀塘瑞和街市後的垃圾站，推着手推車上班。「我5點幾已經起身喇！」許生精力十足。啪一聲，把一塊卡板推倒在手推車上，「拎唔起㗎，我借力擺落去㗎咋，一塊卡板有時成50斤重。」他把叠了兩塊卡板及幾個發泡膠箱的手推車推上斜坡，回到垃圾站。之後再把滿溢的垃圾桶推回來，「最討厭賣魚嗰啲魚腸⋯⋯又腥又臭又重！」大約8時左右，他已經走了三四轉，清不完的垃圾像囤在河流下游、混濁的沙泥⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WNQvy3LI1A0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWNQvy3LI1A0&d=z1Z9%2FhyuGVbDXJZ%2FGqhOoeSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=e5719ba0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WNQvy3LI1A0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">呀伯又準備申請佢大陸老婆來香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家準備好歡迎佢未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似左膠政棍之前成日話清潔工好慘又乜又柒，而家會唔會講2句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"92cd2cc730344b0901804f47bd69e08ea799e3b6","tid":2530664,"uid":219635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7df095bf4ddfb86d7df5e782c838ebb2958a12","tid":2530664,"uid":219635,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:40:21.000Z","msg":"大陸老婆連劏房呀伯都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（呀伯申請咗公屋）"},{"pid":"89c77c193b7af81394a5b970e8cde3d788d077f5","tid":2530664,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c9664baa09c95747d437dadd5d6330e1704b974","tid":2530664,"uid":75823,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"瑞和街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761264773794cc0ebd36a7aad8f48a5097136de0","tid":2530664,"uid":30169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"許生精力十足。啪一聲"},{"pid":"c2e68e50bc82e4402a9eb9cdd185ed63eb3f2105","tid":2530664,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"923c91bc057635d92d9ead9f153c9e5775db23e5","tid":2530664,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"761264773794cc0ebd36a7aad8f48a5097136de0","tid":2530664,"uid":30169,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"許生精力十足。啪一聲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:41:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a78f464734f85109c7fae730a3cdb195c6c405","tid":2530664,"uid":219635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:41:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fa