一眼緩緩開口：「你讓我想到一位失散多年的朋友；他跟我說過一個故事關於他在非洲狩獵時遇上的故事；當時，他在草原上，遇到一頭獅子。他立刻從背上抓下槍來瞄準。<br />\n<br />\n然而，他立刻發現他錯了，他拿到的是雨傘，不是槍！<br />\n這時已經太遲，獅子正站在他面前，就要撲過來。<br />\n他沒辦法，只好把雨傘扛上肩，使盡吃奶的力量『砰！砰！砰！』大叫三聲。<br />\n奇蹟發生了，那獅子竟然倒下來，死掉了。」<br />\n<br />\n「不可能！那一定是別人幹的！」老人大叫<br />\n<br />\n「我也這麼覺得。」醫師冷笑"},{"pid":"7c6e22e900ffcf695a92985c288a1e253fc094e7","tid":2530664,"uid":139663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:59:25.000Z","msg":"各取所需姐"},{"pid":"2428635853c16631a0c29dc9256c6e043ae5bdaf","tid":2530664,"uid":49004,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:59:27.000Z","msg":"連登毒撚老咗就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffdf88859f2a50e92c52a4cf70973984af38060","tid":2530664,"uid":277432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"嫩妻圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8084488d31db8462a8e8988f7c4e161d5d7dcdba","tid":2530664,"uid":344625,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNvNUy8apjXBjAqr2aAm5zt4MFqMR1mwgd7x3gGFWpLhM?filename=P4rgLWL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4rgLWL.gif&h=81bef957&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"834144105edc7ee0b35a0c728d51ddf90cd9fbd9","tid":2530664,"uid":323720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"想30呎住2個人係咩概念？"},{"pid":"322baea11e8a9b55946f16bff5c055a2092affb5","tid":2530664,"uid":269629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25957382d8cf6bc95eef14ee256da9e27e5a6e94","tid":2530664,"uid":86246,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"寧願佢叫雞算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"佢會娶完老婆後繼續叫<img 